 He deserves!', 3301, 0), (192785, 'When you know every well what to do and how to do it, your attitude determines how well you will have it done!', 3301, 0), (192786, 'The kind of death you should mourn over is the one that happen when you abort your potentials prematurely! Life without purpose is a tragedy!', 3301, 0), (192787, 'God doesn''t create imitations, so He designed you naturally. It’s ungratefulness to dream of putting on unnatural self. You have no right to fake God’s design!', 3301, 0), (192788, 'Your mother just carried you literally. The one who really gave you to her is the one who really knows about the main problem you were meant to solve!', 3301, 0), (192789, 'True leadership is an attitude that naturally inspires and motivates others, and it comes from an internalized discovery about yourself.', 3301, 0), (192790, 'If you don’t know your maker, chances are that you will never know yourself. If you don’t know yourself, you will bury your meals and complain of poverty!', 3301, 0), (192791, 'Leaders fail when they begin to fall in love with negative mindsets of other people!', 3301, 0), (192792, 'If you don’t know your maker, you may travel miles to find your true self to no avail. Your maker knows you; to know yourself, know your maker!', 3301, 0), (192793, 'Attitude is that litmus test which differentiates a knower from a doer. Knowers have only the skills', 35207, 0), (192794, 'There are no intermediaries when it comes to matters of change. Anyone who is not for change is against it. Anyone who is against change is an enemy of nature!', 3301, 0), (192795, 'People perish not because of lack of faith', 35208, 0), (192796, 'Wisdom does not only reflect itself in a person’s knowledge of what to say. It appears also in his knowledge about how to say it and when it should be said!', 3301, 0), (192797, 'Rivers don’t drink their own waters', 35209, 0), (192798, 'Great leaders are great servants because the only way of setting an example is by demonstrating an example. Service to mankind is the key to true leadership!', 3301, 0), (192799, 'Dare to rise, when all voices behind you say you can’t get there, ignore them and move on… it’s not about the talents and gifts you have; it’s about how wise you optimize them!', 3301, 0), (192800, 'Every birth comes out of labour pains. The most difficult task is not about being pregnant with visions', 35210, 0);
INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (192801, 'Celebrity mentality sometimes misguides us to make wrong choices. That’s why T.V screens sometimes lie to us!', 3301, 0), (192802, 'You can’t live outside the manual of your manufacturer and perform the function He created you for. God’s word is His manual', 35211, 0), (192803, 'Every true leader is a true follower. Every true follower is a true leader. You are followed because of the dreams you pursue', 35212, 0), (192804, 'Preparation is the key to leadership success. The more prepared you are the less your struggle to make it happen and the more your effectiveness!', 3301, 0), (192805, 'True leaders are ready to sweat when making rehearsal, than to cry tears when actually practicing. To save the tears, be ready to sweat!', 3301, 0), (192806, 'It’s not the public opinion of what you are that matters, but the private personality of who you are!', 3301, 0), (192807, 'Jesus’ promise of resurrection of believers came with a demonstration. He did it and said His followers who die will do same. This is leadership! It’s based on truth!', 3301, 0), (192808, 'You can’t lead if you don’t know what you were made for. You can’t know what you were made for if you don’t ask the one who made you! Know your creator', 35213, 0), (192809, 'Leadership is not a raw gift given to a group of people. It is the product of any type of gift everyone one has. It therefore means, any kind of gift is a leadership gift!', 3301, 0), (192810, 'To know the purpose of a product, you must pay attention to what the manufacturer said about it. What God said about you is that you must have dominion over all other creation. Just pay attention and take the lead!', 3301, 0), (192811, 'The leader’s job is to show the way. The bottom line is that you can’t tell anything about the condition of the way if you''ve not traveled on it yourself!', 3301, 0), (192812, 'You will learn more when you teach someone else. The secret to obtaining more knowledge is teaching more people as possible and available!', 3301, 0), (192813, 'Sometimes it is difficult to different between leaders and misleaders. However, with the measurement of true service to mankind, the evidence is very clear!', 3301, 0), (192814, 'The fact that a seed is viable is not a proof that it’s going to bear good fruits. Some good seeds are destroyed by bad soils. So is leadership; everyone was born to lead, but not all become leaders!', 3301, 0), (192815, 'The sweeper of the street is a leader in his own respect provided he does his job well with all love, diligence and attention than anyone would do when given the same broom sticks.', 3301, 0), (192816, 'Many people know themselves but hardly believe what they know. To be a leader, knowing yourself is not enough; you must believe what you know about yourself!', 3301, 0), (192817, 'Everyone can be a leader irrespective of their age, race, creed, nationality or political affiliation. Once you can figure out your talents and optimize them very well, at the right place and at the right time, you are a leader.', 3301, 0), (192818, 'What people see you do may not be remembered', 35214, 0), (192819, 'Two cool things I like about a great cook and their exquisite dishes...they enjoy cooking it and enjoy watching me eat it!', 11023, 0), (192820, 'March out of the common line; make bold steps ahead and dance to the tune of a sweeter, better and nicer tone of your own music. March out of the tiny box!', 3301, 0), (192821, 'The worst to ever happen to a person who aims at the sky is to fall on the tallest mountain', 35215, 0), (192822, 'The little energy you obtained from your breakfast can ignite your willingness to kick start. Don’t overlook the little energy you have now by fixing eyes on a supposed magical influence farther away!', 3301, 0), (192823, 'You don’t need to travel far to make people happy. When you make people nearer to you happy, people farther away from you will surely come. Keep doing it!', 3301, 0), (192824, 'Low self-esteem is no better home to take a refuge. It does not keep you comforted from any danger', 35216, 0), (192825, 'You may need an additional money to make things happen and have it, but you can have an additional time anywhere. Value your time; as you wait, it is passing!', 3301, 0), (192826, 'People who achieve big things are those who decide to try ideas that were previously rated and graded as impossibilities. “Impossibility” never exists!', 3301, 0), (192827, 'Don’t run away from the gains because it comes with pains. If you ever love to go for the sweet honey, be ready to be stung by a busy bee! Go for it anyway!', 3301, 0), (192828, 'It''s some twisted, limited, grocery-store mentality, where people have to be dairy products or vegetables or frozen foods for us to be able to understand them and feel safe. Maybe we''ve just become such mega-consumers that we can''t deal with anything that''s slightly inconvenient (basically, anything that requires thought). I was the tofu amidst the Baking Products and Cleaning Supplies." (pg. 71)', 202, 0), (192829, 'Impatience has ruined many crowns; it had lured people to give up when they have just few minute to win, just few millimeters to touch the winning carpet!', 3301, 0), (192830, 'You can’t win without being patient. You know why? Success comes when you value time by using it profitably. It comes over time', 35217, 0), (192831, 'Failure is your inability to recognize that you have made the same mistakes again. Making a mistake is normal', 35218, 0), (192832, 'If there is anything in life to worry about at all, it’s your wasted yesterday. Unfortunately, before you worry about it, you have to waste today doing so. Never worry!', 3301, 0), (192833, 'You are likely to fall when you stop paddling your bicycle. Such is life. As long as you don’t give up, you will never end up failing!', 3301, 0), (192834, 'Don’t lose yourself in the process of caring for others. Don’t overdo it as if you don’t need any care to give to yourself. It’s true, you are special too!', 3301, 0), (192835, 'The strongest people are people who faced the toughest situations in life. People who are defeated by the toughest battles are stronger than those who have won by using the escape route!', 3301, 0), (192836, 'Don’t try to prove to everybody that the reason why you can’t is that nobody could. It’s no excuse. You can break the tradition by being the first person to make it happen!', 3301, 0), (192837, 'The brain says “it is impossible” and the legs respond “let’s sit down”. The brain says “it is possible” and the legs respond “let’s go to work”. Don’t blame the legs, blame the head.', 3301, 0), (192838, 'The hills and mountains on your ways are going to be removed. But remember that’s what should happen when God gives you the shovel. Use your gifts', 35219, 0), (192839, 'You can only know how confident you are when you kick-start. True confidence is not found in excessive rehearsals; it comes from experience. Plan, prepare, but will willing to make it happen!', 3301, 0), (192840, 'The devil may not be interested in preventing you from knowing the undone job. What he may do is to make you think it’s somebody’s job and not yours.', 3301, 0), (192841, 'Everything known and referred to as “impossible” is often what has not been attempted before. It will always have a change of name once it’s attempted!', 3301, 0), (192842, 'The grace and mercy by which you are not arrested for not paying your daily oxygen bills, is the grace that is sufficient to take you through successfully. It''s the grace of our Lord Jesus Christ. Enjoy it!', 3301, 0), (192843, 'Before you can brighten the corner where you are, you must first develop dislike for the initial dull corner you once endured. You can’t change what you are comfortable with.', 3301, 0), (192844, 'You may face opposition not only because you are doing something wrong, but because you are doing something right. Not all oppositions are meant for a better life!', 3301, 0), (192845, 'A higher speed on the wrong path is very is fatal! Don’t be desperate about going ahead with the highest speed. First of all, be sure you are on the right track.', 3301, 0), (192846, 'Opportunity never arrives, it only walks by. Chance never comes, it only knocks at the door. Never think the success will jump into your palms; you must work for it!', 3301, 0), (192847, 'Impatience is not the fastest way of getting to where your treasures are. It is the quickest way of by-passing them without even knowing. Keep calm', 35220, 0), (192848, 'I like to compare my mental stress capacity to a dinner plate. Most people have moderate amounts of stress in their life, like a nice balanced meal. The food represents different stresses that occur in our lives, past and present.', 33056, 0), (192849, 'People can poison people', 35221, 0), (192850, 'A hopeful life is a successful life. People who bury their hopes and crave for someone’s success never know that their diamond is hidden as they envy other’s silver!', 3301, 0);
INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (192851, 'Let your first enemy be mediocrity; it has no role to play, no word to say and no action to display in your life. Never love to swim in shallow waters; they breed nothing than fearful reptiles of failure!', 3301, 0), (192852, 'Refuse to be small no matter how many times people insist on squeezing you. The same people who carelessly call you “Hey” are the same people who will cheerfully call you “Hi” when you continue to drive your life positively!', 3301, 0), (192853, 'Pick the axe', 35222, 0), (192854, 'You can’t believe in your dreams if you don’t believe in the giver of the dreams. In all things, put God first. He is willing to put you ahead for excellence!', 3301, 0), (192855, 'One word is enough to destroy an entire city provided that word is backed by anger. Drop down the bullets of anger', 35223, 0), (192856, 'Shake hands with today', 35224, 0), (192857, 'The only way to smile at harvest time is to appreciate the invisible fruits in the visible seed. Hungry people are not those who have no seed. They are those who kill seeds!', 3301, 0), (192858, 'She figured that the main problem in physics is physicists, that most of them are caught in a mind trap because they''re so used to things being made of smaller things. So they instinctively believe that reality, at its most basic level, must be made up of and regulated by almost infinitely small elementary particles.', 35225, 0), (192859, 'Every big castle was once started with a single block', 35226, 0), (192860, 'Make it a promise to be all that you must be. When you dream of reaching the 100th step', 35227, 0), (192861, 'Just look at the track record of these giveaway programs," I protested. "Broken mills, lower production levels of rice after 20 years of work and money. This can''t be right...the only way this will work for the farmers is if they own it themselves, if they can see their own lives getting better because of their efforts and ability to control their own futures and not have to wait around for the government.', 19566, 0), (192862, 'When faced with a problem, don''t keep on discussing it. Go beyond the mental barrier to resolve it.', 35228, 0), (192863, 'Encourage yourself and do it bit by bit. It may appear tough, but every single bite of it every day is an endorsement that all will be chopped off sooner. Nothing is too difficult!', 3301, 0), (192864, 'Lift up your two hands', 35229, 0), (192865, 'Pamper no temptations! Once you are the driver on the steer of your life, choose to knock down every obstacle and challenge on your way to fulfillment.', 3301, 0), (192866, 'It feels great to know that whatever you need to achieve your dreams are in you. Whatever the spider needs to make a cobweb is not in the housefly. Look to yourself', 35230, 0), (192867, 'I love animals, especially with barbeque sauce.', 18341, 0), (192868, 'You care, you dare and you share; this is the unforgettable rule of every true believer and achiever.', 3301, 0), (192869, 'Someone needs your actions to inspire his actions. Never forget, your little broken cake is someone’s daily meal! Care to share you little cake!', 3301, 0), (192870, 'You will rise above all limitations once you begin to live life with the right attitude. People who fail and fall are the people who see difficulties in every opportunity and call it "impossibility". Rise up!', 3301, 0), (192871, 'Change for the better... Let your change be purposeful and determined. Never repeat steps that always make you fail. Never change a step that brings you closer to excellence! You got to make a change!', 3301, 0), (192872, 'Aside your dreams to improve your community, country and continent, dare to save a soul for God. Show compassion, show love... Feed hungry souls and let God be glorified!', 3301, 0), (192873, 'Dare to make it to heaven and in doing so, carry many people along! Be a soul winner!', 3301, 0), (192874, 'All people are standing', 35231, 0), (192875, 'Do well to impress; don''t depress, suppress or oppress anyone. Inspire a soul; never despise!', 3301, 0), (192876, 'You can’t keep your feet on the ground, hoping to enjoy the fruits of your labour. The fruits are on the top; keep climbing till you pluck them with your hands!', 3301, 0), (192877, 'Never say "I don''t care"! We are all looking up to you. Dare to break the fence that confines you! Make it happen!', 3301, 0), (192878, 'The reason why salt and sugar are known to be sweet is that they season other things. Care to share and dare to do it every day!', 3301, 0), (192879, 'There is no harm in trying... Trying improves your skills, enhances your stamina and encourages you to excel. Give it a try... Even in trying moments, keep trying. You will never regret it!', 3301, 0), (192880, 'Stand up for what''s right for you when the time''s right. Wake up to grab it as soon as possible. Shake up when you wake up', 35232, 0), (192881, 'Aspire higher to attain excellence in whatever you do. But be careful when you reach the peak, where the only way is the way downwards. Maintain your standard!', 3301, 0), (192882, 'Fight the good fight of faith', 35233, 0), (192883, 'No one on earth is "functionless". The problem we usually have is that functions of people are being displayed in the wrong positions! Change position!', 3301, 0), (192884, 'People lose their pleasures because they "don''t care". Others misuse their treasures because they "care less". If you''ll win, you must care!', 3301, 0), (192885, 'Your failure may put smiles on people’s faces while your success squeezes tears from their eyes. Don’t be deceived', 35234, 0), (192886, 'Live everyday like your birthday and drive your life with all varieties of appreciation. A life live with thanksgiving every day is never tired of being lived again and again!', 3301, 0), (192887, 'Don’t embrace mediocrity', 35235, 0), (192888, 'If you are going to devote your time to do something you claim you love, take this thought; "Can I pursue this till the end? Am I sure I will never give up on it?" This is persistence.', 3301, 0), (192889, 'If you are going to devote your time to do something you claim you love, take this thought; "am I ready now? When can I begin and have it done without giving up?" This is preparation.', 3301, 0), (192890, 'Take the unpopular route. Use the road no one travels by. Think of doing what is uncommon but remarkable. You have absolutely nobody to overtake you on the empty road!', 3301, 0), (192891, 'Never worry about what others have', 35236, 0), (192892, 'When searching for help, look for the one that will push, not the one that will pull! Your machinery needs a pusher; just avoid every puller and you’ll keep going forward!', 3301, 0), (192893, 'Everyone else believes in you. The major problem is that not all can let you know as in the way you may wish. Some will only let you know through their tests of criticism!', 3301, 0), (192894, 'Nothing is so rewarding than the patience that you take to go over the ramps of life. They may slow you down, but you are an unstoppable hero. Keep driving!', 3301, 0), (192895, 'Spark the dreams you have with integrity and honesty. It’s gonna catch up with excellence if you make it revive in truthfulness in the midst of this world of falsehood!', 3301, 0), (192896, 'The secret for mastery is concentration', 35237, 0), (192897, 'If you are going to devote your time to do something you claim you love, take this thought; "is this going to send me any far? How far can it send me? This is planning.', 3301, 0), (192898, 'If you are going to devote your time to do something you claim you love, take this thought; "is this what I was sent to do? What do I have to have it do well?" This is potential.', 3301, 0), (192899, 'If you are going to devote your time to do something you claim you love, take this thought; "is this productive enough and worthy to be done? How useful will it be?" This is purpose.', 3301, 0), (192900, 'Impression, not oppression determines the real life of a real person.', 3301, 0);
INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (192901, 'No matter how bad you feel, God never sees you as a hopeless person. He may see you as a sinner who needs to be re-washed to get back to his old vision for His purpose, but He will never see you as a hopeless being.', 3301, 0), (192902, 'Hating yourself is like hating what God loves. God loves you, so love yourself and love what God loves.', 3301, 0), (192903, 'The 9th key may be the door opener. Don''t give up after trying the 8th. Keep doing it!', 3301, 0), (192904, 'Never be afraid to try. The only angle through which you can approach success is by the “try-angle”. You may fail if you try, but shame unto you if you don’t try at all. If you fail…rise up and try again and again!', 3301, 0), (192905, 'Be careful you don’t give up on what is yet to give you victory. Many people quit when they were yet to win. Successful people never quit and I believe no quitter had ever been successful too.', 3301, 0), (192906, 'Never despise the talents you have. It is by them that you will do something that has not yet come into existence until you were born.', 3301, 0), (192907, 'It is never too late or too early', 35238, 0), (192908, 'Decide to dream big dreams and make them happen. Never let procrastination and excuses squeeze your dreams to become small. Do it early and do it big!', 3301, 0), (192909, 'Whatever is difficult for you become easy if you take a bite of it every day. Try again and again!', 3301, 0), (192910, 'Mastery is not dispensed on the podium of quitters', 35239, 0), (192911, 'When life gives you a passport dream, order for a reprint. Try again till you have the bigger image. Be passionate you become the real you!', 3301, 0), (192912, 'It is highly impossible for you to be successful at what you don’t love. Do what you love and love what you do.', 3301, 0), (192913, 'When you believe in yourself as a great asset God created for a reason, you will rename your major successes as mere stepping stones because there are greater things that eyes have not yet seen through you, and all are embedded in the value you have in your room; remember that value is you!', 3301, 0), (192914, 'The best decisions you can ever make are the decisions that will guide you to enhance your gifts in order to create a better life for you and others.', 3301, 0), (192915, 'Not now” easily grows to become “never”', 35240, 0), (192916, 'Your success lies in your own hands. You must therefore not wait for the grass to become greener by magic. You have the hands to irrigate your own territory by doing what is expected of you!', 3301, 0), (192917, 'Change anything about your life that cannot be accepted. Accept everything about your life that cannot be changed and move on with your big dreams!', 3301, 0), (192918, 'When it comes to seeing opportunities in the midst of unhopeful situations, the positive brain, (not the pair of eyes) is the sense organ for the sight.', 3301, 0), (192919, 'Ensure that your daily chores, thought, actions, speeches and steps are taken with the purpose of giving you a good brand. Decide to be who God wanted you to be.', 3301, 0), (192920, 'Mostly, people who do not love “change” always go into disagreement when it is suggested. The worst part of the matter that sends their neck veins bulging in vengeance is when that change for progress was meant and would need to affect their position!', 3301, 0), (192921, 'Create an opportunity for change to have way in your attitude and lifestyle. Sometimes, it not us, but our perceptions scare away change!', 3301, 0), (192922, 'Change the size of your dreams if that’s what’s keep you static. Go for bigger dreams, but start in a small way. See the bigger picture and live by the desire to become excellent!', 3301, 0), (192923, 'Don’t forget, success is a product of choices. One of those choices is the willingness to make changes. Make changes and achieve your big dreams!', 3301, 0), (192924, 'Never surround yourself with people who are envious of your ambitions. Decide to be at the right place at the right time and save yourself for greater opportunities.', 3301, 0), (192925, 'Decide be a success; decide to be great, decide to be above average, decide to do the very best of you. Do you know who a P.O.O.R person is? P.O.O.R people are those who are “Passing On Opportunities Repeatedly”!', 3301, 0), (192926, 'You can become good at procrastinating your opportunities by giving flimsy excuses. But never forget that it is rather your success that you are skipping away.', 3301, 0), (192927, 'Accept advice from others and be sure they are positive before you set of to execute them.', 3301, 0), (192928, 'Misery is manifold. The wretchedness of earth is multiform. Overreaching the wide horizon as the rainbow, its hues are as various as the hues of that arch, --as distinct too, yet as intimately blended. Overreaching the wide horizon as the rainbow! How is it that from beauty I have derived a type of unloveliness? --from the covenant of peace a simile of sorrow? But as, in ethics, evil is a consequence of good, so, in fact, out of joy is sorrow born. Either the memory of past bliss is the anguish of to-day, or the agonies which are have their origin in the ecstasies which might have been.', 49, 0), (192929, 'There is no harvest without hard work, therefore never expect chance to solve your problems of abject need for you. You must take deliberate actions!', 3301, 0), (192930, 'Be determined that you will let every dream of yours be released to the fullest capacity. Brighten your picture!', 3301, 0), (192931, 'Where you are now is as a result of either your choice or someone’s choice. If you neglect the ideas of choosing the ultimate things for yourself, someone will hire you by choosing the average thing for you.', 3301, 0), (192932, 'If you think of evil things, you are likely to do evil things and that will never pay you a pesewa. Think of good things and do good always!', 3301, 0), (192933, 'Sometimes, when I''m alone, I wonder if it really counts as being alone, since I am covered in millions of other living organisms.', 15827, 0), (192934, 'Brighten your picture! Refuse to be blurred', 35241, 0), (192935, 'Do not be tired of doing good things. Victory comes after the battle; the crown follows the fight; the same way, behind purposeful actions is a great deal of success. Don’t give up on the fight. Fight till them end; win till all is won.', 3301, 0), (192936, 'The only God who can lead you out of trouble when you are pursuing your dreams is the one who gave you that assignment. Neglecting him from your plans is tantamount to commitment of suicide.', 3301, 0), (192937, 'Choose to be great in your field of choice and work it out. Choose that your harvest will be abundant and strive for it. Choose to be a success and prepare for it. Choose to be a winner and fight for it. Success is a choice!', 3301, 0), (192938, 'It is usual that little streams put their mouths into big rivers. Most rivers can also be traced to the big sea. The fact that you start with a small choice does not mean you will be on that narrow road forever.', 3301, 0), (192939, 'If you fall into the category of people who want to make a great use of their existence, you need to ask yourself these two questions; “what am I doing now”?; “Where is it taking me to?', 3301, 0), (192940, 'Your choices become your directions the moment you start to implement them. When you make choices and you don’t implement them, your choices may be the best ever, but the most useless.', 3301, 0), (192941, 'Whatever you can think about, you can have it realized, provided you can work out the suggestions of your imaginations.', 3301, 0), (192942, 'Your choices are very essential; without a better choice, you are risking to drive a destination whose name you know, but address you forget!', 3301, 0), (192943, 'If you fall into the category of people who want to make a great use of their existence, you need to ask y