neled through a common canal for progress, no condition can alter a single sentence of your success story! Dream it; Drive it; Be in focus!', 3301, 0), (193511, 'If you know the road is steepy with many potholes and curves ahead, you will be informed to drive the car at a required speed. Knowledge is a guide you need to make choices in life.', 3301, 0), (193512, 'Stage fright is very common and could be overcomed through step by step processes, but stuttering is a fright that takes time to conquer.', 332, 0), (193513, 'All achievers had plans that they clearly listed or outlined and run to their fulfillment. If you want to make it as they did, you have to make a plan that defines your purpose; you must write out and clearly define who you are and who you want to be, what you have to do to be that person and how it will be done.', 3301, 0), (193514, 'You need to GIVE UP on methods that always give you wrong results... No matter how committed you are with a wrong formular, it always gives a wrong answer. Give up!', 3301, 0), (193515, 'If you have a plan and you don''t even SHOW IT, you are just like someone born to be great and don''t even KNOW IT.', 3301, 0), (193516, 'If you don''t have a goal, you will score zero even if you run with the fastest speed.', 3301, 0), (193517, 'They may hail you like an Angel. They may claim you are the world''s prince of princes. They may lift you with praise many kilometers above sea level. They may say you are the best of the bests. ....But always remember "you are a human being" with flesh and blood.', 3301, 0), (193518, 'Yes, when you are sharpened with the true information, you will be motivated to make impacts.', 3301, 0), (193519, 'This is God''s beauty!The Elegant nature of Esther,The Meek nature of Moses,The Pius nature of Paul,The Passionate nature of Peter,The Just nature of Jesus and thenThe wise nature of you!', 3301, 0), (193520, 'A good character is not only about the good person people know you to be. Your ability to tell the truth about how bad you had been is also a good character.', 3301, 0), (193521, 'If the problems you have this year are the same problems you had last year, then you are not a leader. You are rather a problem on your own that must be solved.', 3301, 0), (193522, 'The poorest person on earth is not the person who has no job, no cars, no money and no house. The poorest person is the one who has no vision. Visionlessness is poverty in disguise.', 3301, 0), (193523, 'Self-control is a divided battle in one body. The "self" produces desires that "you" must battle with and kick off. Two wrestlers in one body. Just imagine. It''s difficult, though rewarding!', 3301, 0), (193524, 'When you take time to study and practice the word of God, you become like a barrel of great beauty, filled with the energy drink of love with which you inspire people to inspire other people!', 3301, 0), (193525, 'Some people die and you realize that the only mark they left on earth are the tomb stones under which they lie. The impacts you make on earth should be something worthy to improve lives.', 3301, 0), (193526, 'When God calls you to build 100 castles on earth and you built 98, take the 99th as if it''s the begining of your work and work hard to finish the race with all excellence. Go the extra mile!', 3301, 0), (193527, 'A single day in my own shoe that is comfortable for me is better than 365 days in someone else''s shoes that does not fit me at all.', 3301, 0), (193528, 'Run your purpose on the toes of your feet before people can type your success stories with the fingers of their hands.', 3301, 0), (193529, 'Accomplish your tasks by one step at each time. Don''t cut your coat according to your elder brother''s size. Dream big, but start small; do what you can do at a time.', 3301, 0), (193530, 'It''s possible to remain long in the state of deprivation if you are not aware you can escape it. Knowing what exists and who you are is enough to inform you to make ideal choices.', 3301